node.title: Snorkeller dies in Coromandel water incident
node.description: A snorkeller has died in a water incident at Otara Bay in the Coromandel.
node.content:
["A snorkeller has died in a water incident at Otara Bay in the Coromandel.", "", "
File photo. Photo: 123rf.com
", "Emergency services were called to the scene around 2.30pm, where a man was pulled from the water.", "Police said medical attention was administered, but the victim died at the scene.", "The death will be referred to the Coroner."]
